OL,3,C'One life is worth saving': The
OL,4,Cinjured farmer spreading awareness
OL,5,Cabout safety
OL,7,FA farmer who spent three weeks in an
OL,8,Finduced coma after an accident has
OL,9,Fsaid he wants to spread awareness
OL,10,Fabout safety in case it "saves some
OL,11,Fother guy's life".
OL,13,FDennis Minford was knocked down on his
OL,14,Fown farmyard by a tractor reversing a
OL,15,Ftrailer; his injuries included broken
OL,16,Fribs, punctured lungs, and a fractured
OL,17,Fback, pelvis and collarbone.
OL,19,FIt took him nearly a year to get back
OL,20,Fon his feet.
