OL,3,C'One life is worth saving': The
OL,4,Cinjured farmer spreading awareness
OL,5,Cabout safety
OL,7,FHe wanted to speak out to highlight
OL,8,Fthe importance of safety on farms.
OL,10,F"One life is worth saving," he said.
OL,12,FFarming is one of the most dangerous
OL,13,Findustries in Northern Ireland.
OL,15,FIn the last 10 years, 55 people have
OL,16,Fdied in farming accidents; the average
OL,17,Fage of those killed is 63.
OL,19,FPeople like Gemma Mooney are working
OL,20,Fto make farmyards safer.
