OL,3,C'One life is worth saving': The
OL,4,Cinjured farmer spreading awareness
OL,5,Cabout safety
OL,7,FIn her role as an inspector for
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland's Health and Safety
OL,9,FExecutive, she looks at things like
OL,10,Fmachinery and making sure they are
OL,11,Fvisible.
OL,13,FShe said: "It's about trying to get
OL,14,Fthe farmer to think about what they're
OL,15,Fgoing to do with the machinery, making
OL,16,Fsure that the areas that they're
OL,17,Fworking in are as safe as possible,
OL,18,Fmaking sure the machinery is as safe
OL,19,Fas possible."
